<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Did you forget something?</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #333; 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f0e8;
    }
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3d1c, #2d5a27); 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
    }
    .header h1 { 
      color: #7a9e7e; 
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content { 
      background: #ffffff; 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .btn { 
      display: inline-block; 
      padding: 14px 32px; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d5a27, #4a7c44); 
      color: #ffffff; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 30px; 
      color: #666; 
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #2d5a27;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🌿 FRESH HARVEST</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h2 style="color: #1a3d1c; margin-top: 0;">Did you forget something?</h2>
    
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
    
    <p>We noticed you left some items in your cart. Don't miss out on <span class="highlight">fresh, organic produce</span> delivered to your doorstep!</p>
    
    <p>Your cart is waiting for you. Complete your order now and enjoy:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Same-day delivery (for orders before 2 PM)</li>
      <li>100% fresh and organic products</li>
      <li>Earn reward coins with your purchase</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="https://freshharvest.app/cart" class="btn">Complete Your Order</a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
      Need help? Contact us at orders@freshharvest.app or 0113 323 234.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Fresh Harvest Grocery</strong></p>
    <p>Nairobi, Kenya | orders@freshharvest.app | 0113 323 234</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
      You received this email because you have an account with Fresh Harvest Grocery.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
